      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They looked terrific.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They looked incredible-- the whole Bielski brothers-- the whole-- everybody looked terrific.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was sort of-- there was a different-- one can tell different-- absolutely different atmospheres-- it's just incredible-- in one day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because we were already-- or how many times-- how many years?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two years, I think, we spent before we escaped in the-- under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
